addNewText

public void addNewText(java.util.Vector<Point> pointList,
                       java.lang.String textStr)
Method for adding new text in list of strings that describe positions of points that make this NDG condition. Also, best description is updated.

Parameters:
pointList - List of points whose special position generates this NDG condition.
textStr - Text for description of this NDG condition.

populatePointLists

private int populatePointLists()
Method that populates lists of points of this NDG condition object with all combinations of points that could make this NDG condition.

Returns:
SUCCESS if successful, general error code otherwise

checkInParametricObjects

public boolean checkInParametricObjects()
Method that checks polynomial form of this NDG condition in other parametric objects.

Returns:
TRUE if there is some parametric object, FALSE otherwise.

transformToUserReadableForm

public int transformToUserReadableForm()
Method that transforms polynomial form of this NDG condition to user readable form which is stored in text property. If transformation is unsuccessful or impossible, text remains empty and where necessary polynomial will be displayed instead of user readable text.

Returns:
Text associated to this NDG condition is stored in text property; SUCCESS is return if method successfully completes and general error is returned otherwise.
